---
title: Dukkah & Dill-Crusted Salmon with Carrot Fries & Garden Salad
description: Sometimes you want to put dinner in the oven and forget about it. That’s why this clever meal of salmon and sides involves no stove time at all. Both the fun carrot fries and the dukkah-crusted fish are baked, leaving you free to mix up a quick salad and get ready to enjoy the explosion of flavours
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c074a54e3f3393fa417ba73-47dbd214.jpg
